text: MetroPlus em i gutpela moa na i no gat planti manmeri, tasol em i moa ekspensif moa, tasol em i liklik mani moa long ol nomol tiket bilong ol trein i save ron aninit long graun long Europe.
Long mekim dispela yu bai pulapim wanpela pepa wantaim ol lokel polis o go lukim ol ofis bilong 'immigration'.

Olgeta moning. ol manmeri i save lusim liklik kantri taun taim ol i kalap long kar long go long ol ples bilong ol long wok na ol i save abrus ol narapela lain we ples bilong ol long wok i stap long ples we ol i lusim nau tasol na i kam.
Sapos yu no save long draiv long ol rot autsait long siti, yu mas strongim yu yet: i gat ol ples we i sut i go daun o i kam antap, i gat ol liklik rot we i no gat spes long ron, na ol sap kona.
Namba wan 'transportation' em wokabaut, ol manmeri i stat long wokabaut long tupela lek tu miline yia i go pinis taim ol Homo Erectus (dispela em i min olsem 'upright man') i kamap.
Ol lain bilong travel we i plen long go mekim 'sex reassignment surgery' long narapela kantri i mas ol 'valid documents' bilong ol long yusim taim ol i kam bek.

Long narapela taim, ol lain we i stap autsait long ol ples we ol turis i save stap long en em ol i nid long mekim dispela 'registration'. Tasol, dispela i mekim na lo bai i no inap klia, olsem na yu mas painimaut pastaim.
Sapos yu wok long travel i go long wanprla kantri we i wok long divelop yet long namba wan taim – o long wanpeal nupela hap bilong graun – no ken ting olsem yu no inap long kisim 'culture shock'.
Ol meri: Em i gutpela olsem ol meri i we i go long hap i mas tok olsem ol i marit, maski ol i no marit tru tru.

Em i bikpela mani long ol turis long i go na lukim dispela ples. Bodi bilong ol turis i mas fit long i go long dispela hap na ol i ken i go long taim bilong sama long Novemba i go long Febueri, na ol i ken i go long Peninsula, Islands na Ross Sea.
Wanpela raun i go long dispela hap em yu ken bungim i go wantaim wanpela raun long bot i go long raunwara.
Plis tingim olsem yu bai lukim wanpela bikpela matmat we ol i planim planti lain long en, tu dispela ples em i gat bikpela mining long planti manmeri long dispela graun.
Yu mas save olsem taim yu go long ol 'marina' olgeta samting bai kamap ples klia. Yu bai bungim ol narapela lain i save kalap long bot na ol bai serim infomesen wantaim yu.
Wankain, taim yu gat wanpela Schengen visa, yu no nid long aplai long ol visa long wanwan bilong ol Schengen memba kantri, na dispela seivim taim, mani na pepawok.
Dispela em i yu ken mekim wantaim wanpela nomol kar taim yu mekim gut plen, tasol i gutpela moa long yuim 4x4 kar na planti ol hap em yu ken go long en wantaim wanpela 'high wheel base' 4x4.
Long ol rot we i gat sno (snow) o ais, 'friction' em i no strong na yu no inap long draiv olsem yu save draiv antap long kolta nating.
Teksi bilong serim wantaim narapela pasindia em i gutpela rot bilong sindaun gut na i go i kam hariap long ol ples i stap klostu, kain olsem Paro (Nu 150) na Punakha (Nu 200).
Twin Otter i bin wok long traim long 'land' long Kokoda long aste olsem Airlines PNG Flight CG4684, tasol em i no mekim olsem long namba wan taim pinis.
Long ol 'sleeper train' bilong nait, 'conductor' i ken kolektim paspot (passport) olsem na yu ken slip gut na ol i no inap distebim yu.
Dispela bris em ol i makim taim bilong em long op long Septemba 2017, taim ol i pinisim ol 'customs checkpoints' bilong ol Brazil.
No gat 'airline alliance' i karamapim olgeta tripela 'oceanic crossing' insait long Southern Hemisphere (na SkyTeam i no karampaim wanpela bilong ol dispela 'crossing').
Sapos yu stap insait long dispela 'zone', yu ken kalapim boda na yu bai i no inap go long 'passport control checkpoint' gen.

Maski yu ting olsem em i isi long joinim 'airline' we yu save flai planti taim long en, yu mas save olsem ol samting we ol i save givim em i narakain narakain na ol 'frequent flyer points' we ol i save givim aninit long narapela 'airline' em i gutpela moa long wankain 'alliance'.
Sampela ol ‘airline’ i save givim yet ol prais bilong go long funerel (funeral), dispela em i liklik diskaun (discount) long kost bilong ol las minit travel.
Ol turis i ken go lukim ol kainkain 'landmark' bilong wanpela kantri o ol i ken lukluk long wanpela eria tasol.
Bowen Island em i wanpela ailan we planti lain i save long en long kisim wanpela raun long de o wanpela wiken raun na ol i save givim 'kayaking', 'hiking', ol stua, 'restaurant', na moa.

Pasin bilong flai long balus em i ken wanpela ekspiriens wei mekim ol manmeri i gat kainkain krismas na i kam long kainkain ples i pret, bikpela moa em sapos ol i no bin flai bipo o i bin stap insait long wanpela samting nogut we i kamap long balus bipo.
Long mekim sotpela tok, yusim kar bilong yu yet wanpela gutpela rot bilong go graun long rot, tasol em i no wanpela gutpela we bilong mekim "'camp'".
'Registration' wanpela samting yu mas mekim insait long wok bilong 'visa'. Insait long sampela kantri, yu mas 'register' olsem yu i stap na adres we yu bai stap long en wantaim ol lokel atoriti.
Ol wara we i stap insait long ples em ol gutpela samting bilong mekim holide long en.
Ol lain i save karim bek bilong ol narapela ‑ No ken lusim ai long bek bilong yu, bikpela moa em taim yu long lusim wanpela intanesinel boda na i go long hapsait.

Ol Viking i yusim ol wara bilong Russia long go bek long Black Sea na Caspian Sea. Ol hap bilong ol dispela rot bilong travel long wara em ol lain i ken yusim yet. Sekim sapos i gat nid long kisim spesol tok orait, dispela em i hat long kisim.
Bikpela moa em long ol de we yu stat, tingim long amamasim yu yet long ol ' Western-style' na -kwaliti hotel, na ol sevis bilong mekim yu lainim long stap long dispela hap.
Ol sitisen bilong Cuba husat i holim 'US green card' em ol i mas go long wanpela Ecuadorian Consulate long kisim wanpela pepa i tok olsem ol i no gat nid long i gat wanpela pas i askim ol long i go.
Ol i tok olsem planti bilong ol tiket bai i stap namel long ¥2,500 na ¥130,000, olsem na mak bilong wanpela nomol tiket bai i kost olsem ¥7,000.
Ol travela we i go long kantri we i gat bikpela takis sampela taim ol i ken seivim (save) bikpela mani, ol i ken seivim long ol prodak taim olsem ol 'alcoholic beverages' na 'tobacco'.
Na tu, givim kopi bilong polisi/kontek long ol pren we i travel wantaim yu na ol famili o pren long haus we i wanbel long helpim yu.

Europe em i wanpela kontinen (continent) we i liklik, tasol em i gat planti indipenden kantri. Planti taim, long raun i go long planti kantri em bai min olsem yu bai go insait long planti 'visa application' na 'passport control' moa long wanpela taim.

Sierna em i wanpela 'ranger station' we i save givim ples bilong slip na kaikai wantaim 'camping'. La Loena, San Pedrillo, na Los Patos i save givim 'camping' tasol na i o gat sevis bilong givim kaikai.

Ol 'tour' i go long dispela hap em i no bikpela mani long ol bikpela grup, olsem na sapos yu go yu yet o wantaim wanpela pren, traim long bungim ol narapela manmeri na kamapim wanpela grup we o gat foapela o sikspela lain long kisim wanpela gutpela reit (rate).
Yu mas makim Frequent Flyer 'airline' bilong yu gut.

Sapos kantri we yu bai go long en em ol lain i tok save long sampela samting we yu mas lukaut long en, sampela senis bai kamap long 'travel health insurance' o 'trip cancellation insurance' bilong yu.
Kisim kar bilong yu na go long wanpela longpela 'road trip' em i isi long mekim na em bai mekim yu pilim nais.
Mipela i no save bilong wanem na ol mobail fon sevis i strong moa long hia na i no strong long planti ol narapela hap bilong dispela rot, kain olsem Pennsylvania Wilds.

Ol bikpela rot, ol bilding i gat glas long fran na ol stoa bilong tude em ol i gat ol 'red-tiled roof' we i tredisinel, '18th century' maket, na ol olpela 'mosque' na sios, tasol dispela siti em olsem wanpela siti bilong Mediterranean Europe na i no Turkey bilong bipo.
Jerusalem i gat planti ples bilong histori, kalsa na akeoloji (archeology), wantaim planti hap bilong baim samting, baim kaikai, na 'restaurant'.
Long olgeta yia, planti visita i save kisim bagarap long bodi bikos ol i no i stap longwe gut. Ol dispela animal i bikpela, wel, na i ken kamapim birua, olsem na givim ol spes bilong ol.

Yu mas lukim olsem yu save long wanem samting yu ken o i no inap long bringim i go insait long kantri na tokaut sapos mak bilong samting yu bringim em i go antap moa long wanem lo i tok orait long en.
Turkish Airlines i save flai i go long 39-pela ples insait long 30 kantri insait long Africa stat long 2014 i kam inap nau.
Wanpela 'Avenger class mine countermeasures ship', dispela sip i wok long go long Puerto Princesa long Palawan.
Wanpela 'hospitality exchange network' em i wanpela oganaisesen we i save konektim ol travela wantaim ol lokel manmeri long siti we ol bai i go na raun long en.
Bikos ol 'inter-district' bas (bus) i save pulap, em i gutpela long baim wanpela tiket sampela de bipo long taim bilong kalap long bas.
Na tu, ol i save makim ol ‘route’ we planti lain i save go wokabaut o ‘cycling’ long em.
Wankain olsem olgeta South African National Parks, i gat 'conservation' na 'entry fee' bilong wanwan de long ol park.
Dispela trupela komuniti we i stap long Howe Sound autsait tasol long Vancouver, na em i isi long go long en long wanpela 'water taxi' we i save lusim Granville Island ilong 'downtown' Vancouver.

Bilong wanem na ol 'transportation system' i save kamapim ol dispela kain komplen, bilong wanem na ol i no save wok gut long olgeta de? Ol 'transportation engineer' i no save long mekim wok bilong ol? O, i gat samting we i bikpela moa i wok long kamap?

Dispela taun em i stap arere tasol long 'falls', na ol i save pulim planti turis, tasol dispela ples em i gutpela long ol lain i painim 'adventure' na ol lain i laik lukim ol samting long i stap longpela taim.
Ol 'cruise' i go long Saint Petersburg i save givim taim long raun long taun. Ol pasindia bilong 'cruise' i no nid long karim visa (lukim ol 'terms').
Sampela senis o rikwes em yu mas tokim 'travel agent' pastaim na i no go stret long hotel.
Moa long 60-pela 'cruise ship' i save go long ol wara bilongt Galapagos ‑ stat long sais bilong 8-pela pasindia i go long sais bilong 100-pela pasindia.
Sapos as tingting bilong wanpela man o meri long i go long wanpela ples long save long histori na kalsa orait dispela kain 'tourism' em ol save kolim olsem 'cultural tourism'.

Long olpela Medina em i isi long painim ol ples we i save salim ol samting bilong ol Morocco, kain olsem 'tagine', 'pottery', 'leather goods', 'hookahs', na ol kainkain 'geegaws', tasol olgeta dispela samting em i bilong ol turis long baim.
Ol travela husat i no save painim hat long lainim long stap long nupela kalsa i save painim hat long lainim gen hau long i stap long kalsa bilong ol yet.
Long kain olsem tenpela minit bipo long em bai i 'land' long namba tu taim, em i lus.

Lo bilong Ecuador i tok olsem ol sitisen bilong Cuba i mas kisim wanpela pas we i askim ol long go long Ecuador bipo long ol i ken yusim ol intanesinel eapot o ol 'frontier admission points' long kam long em.
Maski sapos yu draiv i go insait long wanpela 'subtropical rainforest', liklik taim we yu opim dua long go insait long kar dispela em i inap taim long ol natnat long go insait long kar wantaim yu.
Ol i givim wara long ol pasindia taim ol i wet i stap long ples we i hot. Mak bilong dispela hot em 90(F)-'degree'.
Tasol, dispela em wanpela samting we yu no ken wari long en, bikos ol turis em ol i save bungim ol wantaim long pulapim ol kar.

Pasin bilong i stap na mekim wok volentia long narapela kantri em i wanpela gutpela we bilong save long narapela kalsa, bungim nupela manmeri, na lainim sampela nupela samting long yu yet, na kisim sampela gutpela tingting na lainim sampela nupela samting.
Planti taim ol 'travel agent' i save wok wantaim wanwan hotel, yu bai lukim olsem yu ken yusim wanpela lokel 'agent' long makim spes bilong stap long o narapela hap, kain olsem ol 'camping ground'.

Sampela bilong ol 'cruise' i save tok olsem ol i karim ol lain i go long Berlin, Germany insait long ol 'brochure' bilong ol. Olsem yu ken lukim long mep (map) i stap antap Berlin i no stap klostu long solwara na wanpela visit long siti em i no stap insait long prais bilong 'cruise'.
Pasin bilong makim spes bipo long travela i go long dispela ples bai mekim tingting bilong ol i stap isi olsem ol bai gat sampela hap bilong slip taim ol i kamap long hap.
Ol nambis, ol 'theme park' na ol 'camp ground' em ol ples we planti ol 'recreation tourist' i save go long en.
Long ol lain i sekrifaisim ol gutpela samting, taim na pasin bilong bihain plen na daunim mak bilong mani i go daun klostu long jiro, lukim 'minimum budget travel'.
Sapos yu gat sampela moa taim bilong travel, sekim hamas totol bilong raun i go long Africa na hamas totol bilong raun long olgeta hap bilong graun.
Ol 'travel agent' i save givim ol offer' we i gat brekfas (breakfast), kar bilong kisim yu i go i kam long eapot o bungim tu ol prais bilong balus tiket na prais bilong hotel.
Dispela balus em i bin i go long Irkutsk na ol soldia we i stap insait long dispela hap i wok long operetim.
Taim yu stap long narapela kantri na kam bek long haus bilong yu, yu senisim pasin bilong yu long bihainim nupela kalsa na yu lusim sampela bilong ol pasin bilong kalsa bilong yu yet.
Dispela em i min olsem yu ken lukim siti we i gat histori bilong en long sampela de taim yu kam bek long nait na slip long sip.
'Architecture' em i wok bilong disainim na konstraktim ol bilding. 'Architecture' bilong wanpela ples i save kamap olsem samting we i save pulim ol turis i go long em.
Ol ‘airline’ i save givim ol dispela dikaun (discount) em include Air Canada, Delta Air Lines, Lufthansa long ol ‘flight’ i kam long U.S o Canada, na WestJet.
Wanpela 'immigration checkpoint' em i namba wan stop taim yu kam daun long wanpela balus, sip, ol narapela trenspot (transport).
Sampela hotel i gat wanpela 'heritage' i kam long taim bilong ol 'steam railways' na 'ocean liners'; bipo long Second World War, long '19th' o stat bilong '20th century'.
Goma em i wanpela siti we ol turis i save laik i go long en insait long Democratic Republic of Congo long hap ist klostu long kantri Rwanda.
Ol dispela samting we ol i mas mekim em i bilong mekim wanpela gutpela balens i kamap long namba bilong ol manmeri i go i kam long dispela tupela kantri.
Maski em i liklik, em i mekim sampela ol lain we i bin go lukim Hawaii bipo long em i kamap olsem wanpela steit (state) na i no gat ol bikpela hotel bilong turis na ol narapela divelopmen.
'Nature-based tourism' em i save pulim ol manmeri we i intres long lukim ol eria bilong 'nature' na amamas long lukim ol ples, wantaim ol plent (plent) na animal bilong dispela eria.
Long narapela sait bilong dispela samting, ol kondisen bilong ais na sno (snow) em i nomol long planti kantri, na ol kar i save ron i go i kam gut long olgeta de bilong yia.
Ol Safari em ating ol i nambawan samting we i save kisim ol turis i go long Africa na ol i bikpela samting long planti ol visita.
Angkor Pass em yu bai nidim long i go insait long tempel olsem na no ken lus tingtin long bringim paspot (passport) i go wantaim yu taim yu golong Tonle Sap.
Ol visita (visiter) we i no gat inap taim bilong raun i ken spendim taim bilong ol long sampela narapela hap.
Finland em i wanpela gutpela kantri bilong raun long bot. Dispela "'Ples bilong tausen raunwara'" i gat planti tausen ailen insait long ol raunwara na long ol solwara.
Ol i ken mekim wanpela 'reservation' bilong yu sapos yu nidim taim long tingting long 'offer' o kisim ol narapela dokumen long go long dispela ples (eksampel, 'visa').
Ol dispela samting we lo i tok long mekim em i senisim bihainim wanem kantri wanpela travela i go long em pinis o i laik go long en.
Dispela i ken kamapim birua, sapos travela (traveller) i bihainim ol dispela 'mirage', em bai westim eneji bilong em na ol wara we em i gat.
Sapos yu bai go autsait na mekim kem, bringim wanpela bet bilong kem o wanpela 'hammock' long mekim yu i stap longwe long ol snek, 'scorpion' na kain olsem.

Sno bilong em i gat ol hol i go insait long graun na i gat ol plak i makim ol dispela hol. Ol spesol trakta (tractor) tasol i ken ron antap long em na pulim ol plang we i gat saplai na 'fuel' i stap antap.
CafeNet El Sol i save givim wanpela 'reservation service' long wanpela prais bilong US$30, o $10 long ol 'one-day pass'; ol tok save i stap long Corcovado pes bilong ol.

Long bikpela rot bilong lukim samting, ol i kam aninit long tupela grup: Yu ken wok taim yu raun o traim na daunim mak bilong mani yu spendim. Dispela hap toktok bai lukluk long pasin bilong daunim mak bilong mani yu spendim.
Insait long dispela 'transport shuttle' olgeta lain i konek wantaim, na ol i sapotim wanpela 'transport system' we ol 'private car' i kamapim.
'Traffic Flow' em i stadi bilong muvmen (movement) bilong wanwan draiva na kara namel long tupela poin na wanem kain samting ol i save mekim long wanpela narapela.

Maski yu bai no inap long nidim wanpela 'visa' long mekim ol sotpela visit long sampela kantri olsem wanpela turis o go long mekim wok bisnis, taim yu go olsem wanpela intanesinel sumating em yu bai stap longpela taim moa long sapos yu go olsem wanpela turis nating.

Ol nupela samting insait long wanpela kantri we i wok long divelop yet i bin daunim planti bilong ol gutpela travela (traveler), long wanem ol i nid long mekim planti liklik senis long kalsa na ol dispela liklik senis i bung wantaim na i kamap olsem bikpela samting tumas.
Na tu, i gat sampela bas (bus) i save go long hap not long Hebron, dispela em i ples we ol i planim ol papa bilong bilip insait long Baibel Abraham, Isaac, Jacob, na ol meri bilong ol.

Sapos wanpela 'rider' i pundaun long wanpela hos, tasol lek bilong em i pas long 'stirrup', hos i ken pulim ol taim em i ranawe. Long daunim mak bilong dispela hevi long kamap, ol 'rider' i mas mekim samting long abrusim dispela.
Ol bai givim wanpela list bilong ol 'host'long intanet/bilong printim, sampela wantaim 'reference' na 'review' we ol narapela travela (traveller) i givim.
Em i gutpela we bilong yusim gut bajet (budget) na mekim yu i ken i stpa longpela taim long wanpela hap bikos planti ol wok volentia i save givim rum na kaikai na wanpela liklik pe.
Na tu, yu bai i no inap long lukluk gut taim sno (snow) i pundaun o blo o win i kamap wara o i kamap ais long ol windua bilong kar.
'Car camping' em i isi long mekim sapos yu gat wanpela bikpela 'minivan', SUV, Sedan o Station Wagon we i gat sit bilong putim go daun.
Planti ol distrik em planti ol Japanese Coaster Buses i save ron long en, na yu bai sindaun gut.
Dispela bas i bin laik go long Six Flags St. Louis in Missouri long wanpela 'band' long pilai long wanpela bikpela lain manmeri we i baim olgeta tiket.

Tasol, Star Alliance i save karamapim olgeta samting, wanpela samting tasol em i no karamapim em 'eastern' South Pacific long Santiago de Chile i go long Tahiti, dispela em i wanpela LATAM Oneworld flight.
Long intanesinel level, i gat kain olsem 200-pela 'running tour' oganaisesen. Planti bilong ol i save operet long ol yet.
Hong Kong Island i givim teritori (territory) bilong Hong Kong nem bilong na em i ples we planti turis i save go long en.
Taim yu bin i go long narapela kantri long namba wan taim tru, yu bin isi na traim long lainim samting, yu save olsem ol travela i stap long narapela kantri i mas senisim tingting na pasin bilong ol.
Dispela hap tok 'safari' we planti lain i save yusim em i toktok long travel long graun long lukim ol narakain animal bilong Africa, planti bilong ol em ol animal bilong 'savanna'.
Sapos yu go sua long sait bilong wara wantaim ol 'shipboard excursion' yu bai no gat nid long i gat wanpela narapela visa (dispela em i stat long 2009).
Ol 'hostel' em i bilong ol yanpela manmeri – wanpela 'guest' bilong en em bai stap long mak bilong ol twentipela krismas – tasol yu ken painim ol olpela travela tu i stap long hap.
Taim yu stap tasol long haus na holide, yu gat taim long mekim yu yet amamas na kisim sampela taim long mekim wanpela naispela ti o kofi.
Planti manmeri i save makim ples bilong ol bipo yet (bikos ol bot i save pulap long taim we planti manmeri i save laikim).
Ol i yusim ol 'dump truck' long blokim ol maus bilong ol tanel (tunnel ) we i go insait na 80-pela polis manmeri i helpim ol long salim ol ol kar i go long ol narapela rot.
Long taim bilong turis long i go raun long ol stesin i stap long maunten i save kamap long bikpela mak tru long sama (summer) taim bilong India.
Isipela we bilong statim bisnis bilong 'travel writing' em long stretim pasin bilong yu long rait taim yu statim wanpela 'travel blog' websait.
Wanwan taim i save i gat balus i go long insait bilong Antarctica long ol lain bilong klaimim maunten o bilong i go long Pole. I gat bikpela 'base' i stap long Pole.
Husat lain i mekim plen long go long wanpela kantri we woa i save kamap lng en i mas kisim treining (training) i kam long ol profesenol.
Dispela em i gutpela sans bilong lukim Aurora borealis, taim skai bai tudak long klostu olgeta aua long kilok.
Maski 'immigration check' em i no save stap o i no save kamap taim yu kam bek long kantri bilong yu, 'customs control' em i ken hat wok liklik.
I no gat ripot bilong longpela 'traffic delay' long 'bletway', dispela narapela rot bilong go long siti.
Sapos yu go raun na lukim Greenland long taim bilong kol em i impoten olsem yu mas kisim kol klos, (tingim taim yu go moa long hap not, ples bai i kol moa).
Lukluk long wanem ol raun ol 'agent' i wok long mekim promosen long en, maski em long wanpela websait o long wanpela windua bilong stoa.
Schengen zone, em i narakain, sampela taim em i save stap olsem wanpela kantri bilong em yet.
Em i wanpela bilong ol bikpela samting we i save pulim ol turis i go long South Africa na ol i save lukim em olsem impoten samting insait long South African National Parks (SANParks).
I gat kainkain senis i ken kamap, tasol dispela em i ol samting we planti manmeri i save mekim taim ol tok olsem ol "i go long Disney World".
MetroRail i gat tupela level long ol trein bilong i go i kam long wok na raun long Cape Town: MetroPlus (em ol i save kolim olsem First Class) na Metro (ol i save kolim Third Class).
I gat strongpela tok save i go long ol travela long save long ol weda (weather) we i save kamap long ol eria bikos ol bai mekim senis i kamap long ol plen bilong ol travela.

Taim ol animal i lukautim ol dispela pikinini, ol dispela 'feral' pikinini save soim ol pasin (we ol inap long mek) we i wankain olsem pasin bilong dispela animal we i lukautim ol, kain olsem pret o i no save wanem samting bilong mekim taim em i stap wantaim ol narapela manmeri.
'Fission bomb' em i save wok bihainim lo we i save kisim eneji na kamapim wanpela 'nucleus' wantaim planti 'protons' na 'neutrons'.
Retpela tait em wanpela 'marine organism' we i gat wanpela 'cell' na i save stap long graun i save kamapim, taim i gat planti moa bilong dispela 'organisim' we ol i kolim Karenia brevis.
Sapos yu lukluk long ol samting i stap aninit long wanpela 'microscope', yu bai lukim olsem ol i gat planti ol samting we i luk olsem ol liklik bal o liklik 'square'.
Blut i save lusim hat long ol tiub (tube) ol i kolim ol 'artery' na ol i save kam bek long hat long ol tiub (tube) ol i kolim 'veins'. Ol liklik tiub tru em ol i kolim 'capillaries'.
Dispela 'algae' i save kamapim wanpela 'neurotoxin' we i ken mekim 'nerve' insait long ol manmeri na ol pis long i no wok.
Sampela saintis i ting olsem ol Triceratop i bin kaikai ol 'cycad', wanpela kain plent (plant) we i save gro long planti hap long Cretaceous.
Ol plent (plant) i save mekim kaikai bilong ol long san taim 'photosynthesis' i kamap. Ol i save givim seid (shade).
'Roar' bilong taiga em i wankaim olsem 'full-voiced roar' bilong wanpela laion, tasol em i klostu i laik wankain olsem wanpela sentens bilong man i pulim win taim em kros na singaut.
Hershey na Chase i bin yusim 'phages', o ol vaires (virus), long putim DNA bilong ol yet i go insait long wanpela 'bacterium'.

Ol lain i mekim risets long Princeton University long United States na Uppsala University long Sweden i mekim ripot long wanpela nupela 'specie' we i kamap insait long tupela generesen (generation), tasol ol i ting long dispela proses (process) i kisim longpela taim moa, em i kamap bikos long 'breeding' i kamap namel long Darwin finch bilong dispela eria, Geospiza fortes, na cactus finch we i kam long narapela eria, Geospiza conirostris.
Dispela wok em ol i wokim long kamapim sampela as tingting, tasol ol i bin raitim dispela progrem long soim ol samting we ol i bin lukim long Sagittarius 'galaxy'.

Ol manmeri i bin save long ol bikpela kemikel elemen (chemical element) kain olsem gol, silva, na kopa (copper) long bipo taim, bikos ol i bin painim ol insait long envairomen long 'native form' na em i isi long painim ol wantaim ol tul (tool) bilong bipo.
Planti ol 'research telescope' em ol i bikpela fesiliti (facilty) we i stap long ol longwe ples long ol gutpela 'atmospheric condition'.
Dispela impoten hap bilong 'circulatory system' em i hat, we i save pamim blut.

Ol i painimaut olsem Sun i save ol wankain bikpela tingting olsem ol narapela sta: Dispela ektiviti bilong olgeta sta long sistem em ol i painimaut olsem 'luminosity' na 'rotation' bilong ol i save mekim ol i tanim tanim, na i no gat narapela samting gen.
Yumi no inap long save, tasol ating em i gat fok tang. Em i save kaikai trausel, bikpela fis, ol narapela mosasaurus, na ating em i save kaikai ol manmeri tu.

Dispela 'blade' i satp long wanpela 'ice skate' bilong tude i gat 'double edge' na i gat wanpela hol i stap namellong dispela tuple 'edge'. Dispela tupela 'edge' i save mekim isi long 'blade' i holimpasim ais, maski taim em i tanim liklik.
Aninit long ol em ol namel sais pusi we i save kaikai ol namel sais abus stat long rebit (rabbit) i go long entelop (antelope) na dia (deer).

Ol plent (plant) i save mekim 'oxygen' we yumi ol manmeri i save pulim win long en, na ol i save kisim 'carbon dioxide' we yumi ol manmeri i save rausim i kam autsait long bodi bilong yumi (dispela em, taim win we yumi i pulim i go insait i kam autsait).
Long taim bilong winta (winter), amamas wantaim sampela nambawan ples bilong ski long North America, na long sama (summer) traim sampela trupela 'mountain biking'.
'Skiing' em i wanpela ektiviti bilong raun we ol lain i save laik long mekim, ol i kolim "'ski bums'," ol i save plenim holide bilong ol long mekim 'skiing' long wanpela lokesen.

Golf em i wanpela geim (game) we tupela pleiya (player) i save yusim ol 'club' long paitim ol bal i go insait long ol hol.
Em i bin stat long Barcelona's Running Tours Barcelona na Copenhagen's Running Copenhagen, Running Tours Prague we i stap long Prague na ol narapela i hariap long joinim em.

Wanpela 'sport' bilong tude ol i kolim 'fencing' em ol i save pilai long planti level, stat long ol sumatin long univesiti (university) na i go long Olympic kompetisien (competition).
Ol 'sport' we planti manmeri i save long en em 'football', 'basketball', 'volleyball', 'water-polo', 'fencing', 'rugby', 'cycling', 'ice hockey', 'roller hockey' na 'F1 motor racing'.
Bihain long resis we i kamap long Trinde, Carpanedo i pilai wanpis insait long tupela narapela resis long dispela Championships.

Dustin "Goldust" Runnels i tok olsem "Luna i save mekim ol kainkain samting olsem mi…ating em i winim mi…laikim em na misim (miss) em…mi bilip olsem em i stap long gutpela ples."

Dispela tingting bilong 'skiing' em i bilong bipo yet – i gat ol peinting (painting) long hol bilong ston we i soim ol lain i ski long taim i go bek olsem 5000 BC!

Wanpela long tim bilong em Fernando Alonso i stap long fran olgeta taim insait long resis, tasol em i stop long resis taim em i mekim wanpela 'pit stop', i luk olsem dispela i kamap biko long wanpela fran wil (wheel) we ol i no putim gut.
I save i gat etinpela 'medal' tasol bilong winim long wanwan de, sampela kantri i no bin winim wanpela 'medal' na go long 'medal podium' long kisim.

Disaplin (discipline) bilong defens, we ol i wok long hendelim bal na gutpela tim wok i mekim ol i pilai gut tru na olgeta lain i save olsem ol narapela tim i mas traim long winim ol.
Dispela Go Running Tours, we i kisim ples bilong Global Running Tours i save bungim planti bilong ol 'sightrunning provider' long foapela kontinen (continent).

long namba tu gol bilong dispela nait we i bin namba 60 gol bilong em long dispela sisen (season), dispela i mekim em i kamap olsem namba wan pleiya long putim 60-pela o moa gol long wanpela sisen, bihain long Jaromir Jagr na Mario Lemieux tupela i bin mekim dispela long yia 1995-96.

Long wanpela 'hike' long wanpela isipela rot em i no gat nid long redi, na wanpela man o meri we i stap helti i ken amamas long wokabaut long en.

Long dispela taim em i stap wantaim dispela tim, em i skorim (score) 403-pela gol insait long 468-pela taim we em i pilai.

Massa bai i no inap long pilai long olgeta sisen (season) bilong 2009 o moa.

Insait long wanpela wok patnasip (partnership) bilong NPWS and the Sporting Shooters Association of Australia (NSW) Inc, ol volentia we i kwalifai (qualify) em ol i rikrutim (recruit) ol aninit long 'hunting progrem' bilong Sporting Shooters Association.

ASUS Eee PC, we ol i bin mekim presentesen bilong em i go long olgeta hap bilong graun bikos em i ken seivim man na em i ken mekim planti impoten wok, em i kamap olsem wanpela bikpela topik we ol lain i wok long toktok long em long 2007 Taipei IT Month.
Wanpela 'satellite phone' em i no inap long kisim ples bilong wanpela mobail fon, bikos yu bai nid long sanap autsait na yu mas lukim olsem 'satellite' i stap ples klia na yu ken ring.

Nau ol i save yusim dispela AI sistem insait long ol eria bilong 'economics', 'medecine', 'engineering' na 'military', na ol i bin yusim em long bildim sampela komputa bilong haus na 'video game software applications'.

Long kainkain hap bilong United States of America, i gat kain olsem 400,000 'case' bilong Multiple Sclerosis (MS), mekim em i kamap olsem nambawan 'neurological disease' insait long ol bikpela manmeri.
Taim em i wok long haus sik Liggins i stat long mekim investigesen (investigation) long 'premature labour' long taim bilong em yet.
Maski tripela lain i bin stap insait long haus taim dispela kar i bamim, no gat wanpela bilong ol i kisim bagarap.

Wanpela marasin we ol i wok long testim, em i daunim namba bilong ol manmeri i wok long dai long Ebola. Long dispela taim i kam inap nau, i no gat marasin i soim ples klia olsem em i inap long oraitim dispela sik.
Planti tausen 'case' ol i bin ripot olsem em i kamap long ol manmeri, tasol sampela bilong ol i bin kamapim bikpela bagarap.

Oliver Sacks, insait long pepa we em i raitim The President's Speech, em i soim hau olsem manmeri i no inap long klia gut long mining bilong toktok bikos ol i gat sampela bagarap i kamap long brein (brain) bilong ol tasol ol i klia stret sapos man em i tok tru.
Wanpela 'contagious' sik em i wanpela sik we i isi tru long kalap i go long narapela man o meri taim yu stap klostu long wanpela man o meri i gat dispela sik.
Danielle Lantagne, em i wanpela savemeri bilong UN long sait bilong sik, em i tok olsem dispela sik i mas stat wantaim ol 'peacekeepers'.

Tasol, pesentes (percentage) bilong XDR-TB insait long wanpela grup manmeri wantaim sik 'tuberculosis' i stap daunbilo' 60,00 bilong 330,00 manmeri i save kisim dispela sik long wanpela taim insait long South Africa.
MS em i wanpela sik we i save kamap long 'central nervous system', dispela sistem em brein (brain), 'spinal cord' na 'optic nerve' i kamapim.
'Sleep interruption' em i pasin bilong kirap namel long slip na go bek long slip sotpela taim bihain (10–60 minit).
Na tu, long ol ples we i hot ol bekteria (bacteria) i ken gro hariap moa na stap longpela taim autsait long bodi.
Long wanpela intaviu, em i tok olsem dispela nupela 'variant' i bin "kamapim bikpela hevi na pret bikos long planti manmeri i dai."
Long sama (summer), yu bai nid long lukaut long ol natnat sapos yu tingting long wokabaut i go insait long renfores (rainforest).
Na bihain ol i salim em i go long Addenbrooke's Hospital long Cambridge.
Dr. Tony Moll i painimaut long dispela Extremely Drug Resistant Tuberculosis (XDR-TB) long KwaZulu-Natal rijen bilong South Africa.

Dispela 'strain' bilong 'bird flu' em i nogut tru long ol manmeri, H5N1, na ol savemanmeri i tokaut olsem trutru dispela sik i go long wanpela wail pato na em i dai, na ol i painim em long Mande, long ol ples tais klostu long Lyon long hap is bilong France.
I gat ol planti kainkain konstraksen bilong ol ai, we i bihainim wanwan samting i stap insait long wanpela animal o bihainim wanem samting dispela animal i nidim.
Ol nambawan samting we i soim olsem 'internal poisoning' i kamap em wanpela kontena bilong marasin o 'toxic chemical' bilong haus i op na i stap.
I luk olsem sampela bilong ol sikmanmeri i bin kisim dispela binatang long haus sik, Dr, Moll i ting olsem, na tupela bilong ol lain em ol wokmanmeri bilong haus sik.
Dispela sik em ol pik i save karim, na ol moskito i save kisim long pik na givim i go long ol manmeri.
Risets i bin painimaut olsem sans bilong ol meri long kisim MS em i tupela taim moa long ol man.
Ol 'spirit' we lo i tok tambu long en i gat ol kainakin samting insait long en wanpela em 'methanol', dispela i ken kamapim aipas na dai maski yu dring liklik tasol.
Insait long ol 'structured PA session' we i wok long kamap long olgeta wik, ol i lukim olsem dispela senis i kamap bikos long 'catastrophizing', na i no long 'depression' na pasin bilong pret.
Taim planti manmeri i gat kar, planti eksiden i ken kamap long ol rot, dispela bai i mekim na ol lain bai i kamapim ol nupela teknik insait long heltkea long stretim ol bagarap long bodi.

Ol lain i go pas long wok painimaut i tok olsem dispela i ken mekim ol kantri we i no gat planti mani long ditektim sik kensa, TB na malaria. Long dispela ol kantri mak bilong ol lain we i save winim ol sik kain olsem kensa bilong susu em i hap namba tasol bilong ol lain bilong kantri we i gat planti mani.

Dr. Ehud Ur, em i wanpela profesa bilong marasin long Dalhousie University long Halifax, long Nova Scotia na em i siaman sains na klinik seksen bilong Canadian Diabetes Association i givim tok lukaut olsem dispela risets i nupela yet.

Ol dispela pikinini i save laik long i stap insait long planti trabel, bikos ol i save "mekim ol 'risky behavior', stap insait long ol pait, salensim atoriti" long kirapim brein (brain) bilong ol, bikos ol nomol samting i no save kirapim brein bilong ol.
Ol manmeri i ken kisim bagarap long dispela taim ol i pulim win bilong dispela wara we win na sibruk i karim i kam.
Sampela manmeri i bilip olsem taim yu lukim planti driman we i no tru long planti taim dispela i ken mekim yu i pilim tait nogut tru.
Potro i kisim wanpela tritmen long solda (shoulder) bilong em long dispela taim na i go bek long pilai.
Na moa yet, sapos ol i no inap long mekim dispela ol bikpela samting i ken kamap: 'growth depression', 'malnutrition', na bikpela tru em i dai.

Ol ofisa bilong Armsterdam siti na Anne Frank Museum i tok olsem dispela diwai em wanpela 'fungus' i bagarapim em na em i ken kamapim bagarap long helt bilong pablik taim ol i tok olsem em i laik pundaun.
Dispela haus sik i bihainim rot bilong banisim ol yet long binatang nogut, na ol i putim dispela sikman longwe long ol narapela sikmanmeri long banisim em long givim dispela sik i go long narapela.

Institut bilong Haiti long Justice na Democracy i bin mekim wanpela stadi bilong em yet we i painimaut olsem ol soldia bilong kantri Nepal insait long dispela grup bilong 'peacekeeping' i no save na i karim dispela sik i kam long Haiti.
Ol sik we i save kalap hariap, o ol animal we i save bagarapim ol kilim ol manmeri wantaim fos, em ol i no kam aninit long dispela nem 'pest'.

Ol pikinini we i gat ADD i save painim hat long 'focus' long ol samting olsem skul wok, tasol ol i ken konsentret (concerntrate) long ol samting we ol i save amamas long mekim kain olsem pilai ol geim (game) o lukim katun (cartoon) we ol i save laikim o raitim ol sentens we i no gat 'punctuation'.
Insait long wanpela yia, wanpela man o meri we i sik wantaim dispela binatang i ken givim dispela sik i go long 10 o 15-pela lain we i save stap klostu long ol.

Taim dispela pait i pinis bihain long ol i karim ol lain i kisim bagarap i go long haus sik, kain olsem 40-pela bilong ol narapela kalabus lain i stap autsait na i no laik long go bek long sel (cell) bilong ol.
Emperor Augustus i kisim ol dokta long wok insait long dispela na em i kamapim tu namba wan Roman Medical Corps bilong yusim bihain long taim bilong pait.
Tasol, draiva bilong kar i kisim ol bikpela bagarap long het.
"Nau mipela i gat wanpela rat we i no gat sik suga moa na em i gat 4-pela mun," dispela man i tok.
'Internal poisoning' em i no inap long kamap ples klia hariap. Ol sain, kain olsem traut em ol bikpela sain taim ol lain i no inap long mekim wanpela 'diagnosis' hariap.

Bikos long longpela distens (distance) long kontinen (continent) ol 'mammal' i no inap long mekim longpela wokabaut na dispela i mekim 'giant tortoise' i kamap olsem nambawan animal bilong kaikai gras insait long Galapagos.

Taim yumi skelim olgeta samting, yumi mas no ken kirap nogut sapos ol tumbuna bilong ol i stretim ol "problem bilong 'protein'" bilong ol long wankain we olsem ol 'chimps' long 'savanna' i save mekim long tude.
Em i gutpela long wanpela long baim wanpela Wild Card, we i save givim tok orait long i go insait long ol park insait long South Africa o olgeta South African National Parks.
Dispela hap tok i kisim mining bilong em long Bed-bugs, ol dispela binatang we i save parasait long ol manmeri.
Ol i stap kol moa long ol ples we i raunim ol long san na long nait ol i hot moa long ol ples we i raunim ol.
I no olsem ol narapela 'primates', ol 'hominid' i no yusim han bilong ol long muv o karim hevi o swing namel long ol diwai.
Ol wol na ruf bilong ol ‘ice cave’ i ken pundaun na i ken pasim ol ‘crack’.

Planti savemanmeri i lukim olsem ol 'rhythm' we i kamap long bodi na pasin bilong ol animal na manmeri i save bihainim ol 'cycle' bilong ol samting we i stap autsait long bodi na ol 'biological clock' bilong bodi.
Tasol narapela sait, em i bikos mak bilong wara em i bikpela tru olsem na yu bai no inap long lukim Falls—bikos sais bilong wara i blokim ples bilong lukluk!
Ol animal i stap long olgeta hap bilong graun. Ol i dik i go insait long graun, ol i swim long solwara, ol i flai long skai.
'Moose' (narapela nem bilong en em 'elk) em ol i no save pait wantaim fos, tasol ol i save banisim ol yet long samting we ol i ting olsem i ken bagarapim ol.
Ol man i stat long lukautim meme long kain taim olsem 10,000 yia i go pinis long Zagros Mountains bilong Iran.
Ol 'rip currents' em ol tait bilong solwara we i bruk long nambis na i wok long kam bek, planti taim long wanpela rip o kain samting olsem.

Ol fosil (fossil) bilong bun bilong han we i bilong tu milien o tri milien yia i go pinis i soim olsem i gat senis i kamap long wok bilong han we ol i bin yusim long muv na nau ol i yusim long mekim ol samting.

Ol i ken lukluk gut tru long tudak wantaim 'night vision', na tu, ol i save muv isi tru. Ol 'ocelot' i save painim kaikai bilong ol taim ol i hait wantaim ol samting i stap long envairomen na kalap antap long animal we ol i laik ketsim.
Ol 'box jellyfish' i save kamap olgeta taim arere long nambis na arere long ol maus wara long Oktoba i go long Epril long hap nat long 1770. Sampela taim ol i ken kamap autsait long ol dispela taim.
Ol nambis bilong Tamaki Drive i stap long Waitemata Harbour, long ol 'upmarket' komuniti bilong Mission Bay na St Heliers long Central Auckland.
Ol dispela plent (plant) i luk olsem ol liklik pam (palm) diwai we i gat 'crown' we ol longpela sap lip i kamapim.
Problem em i olsem sno em i 'sticky', olsem na em i nidim sampela samting long mekim em i kam daun, na taim sampela sno i kamdaun dispela i ken mekim na olgeta sno i kam daun.

Ol 'periodic rhythms', em ol i no kamap bikos long ol samting we i stap autsait tasol, dispela em ol lain i bin stadi na lukim olsem em i kamap long planti ol samting we i gat laip, wantaim ol 'bacteria', 'fungi', plent (plant) na animal.
Dispela eria em i ples bilong ol kainkain animal na pisin.
'Wildlife photography' em wanpela samting we mipela i no save tingim hatwok i stap baksait long dispela, tasol wankain ol olgeta narapela foto, wanpela piksa em i inap long tausenpela wod.
Bikos long dispela, tupela 'specie' bilong pis i pinis olgeta, na tupela narapela em klostu i laik pinis olgeta, wanpela bilong ol em i 'humpback chub'.
Planti taim, ol pis i save dai bikos i gat planti bilong ol dispela posin samting insait long ol wara.

Dispela plent (plant) we i stap long dispela hap em ol 'protein' i save stap insait long ol lip na ol bin bilong en, tasol dispela em i hat long ol bel bilong ol 'primate' olsem mipela long brukim i go daun na ol i mas kukim ol pastaim.
Montevideo em i stap insait long 'subtropic'; insait long ol mun bilong sama (summer), tempritsa (temperature) bilong em i save stap antap long +30°C.
Ol dispela graun i save kamapim ol 'sandbars' na ol nambis, we i save stap olsem ol ples bilong ol kainkain animal bilong bus.
Ol hotpela deset (desert) tru i ken kamap kol nogut tru long nait. 'Hypothermia' i ken kamap sapos ol lain i no gat kol klos.
Ol 'army colony' bilong ol anis tu i save mas na mekim haus long ol kainkain 'phase'.
Bikos Montevideo i stap saut long Equator, em i save sama (summer) long hap taim em i winta (winter) long Northern Hemisphere na bihain em i save senis gen.
Sampela taim, nambawan samting we i mekim dispela em i san we i mekim sno i hat, sampela taim em sampela moa sno i pundaun, na sampela taim em ol narapela samting, bikpela moa em ol manmeri.
Ol klaut long skai i mekim ol i paul sapos volkeno i bin pairap pinis, o nogat.
Wanpela gutpela 'athlete', taiga i ken klaim (em i no save klaim gut tumas), swim, kalap long bikpela mak na pulim ol samting wantaim strong we i faivpela taim moa long strong bilong man.
Dispela hap tok 'bug' em ol entomolojist (entomologist) i save yusim long toktok long dispela grup bilong ol binatang.
Taim ol man i kam long Galapagos, planti 'mammal' we ol i bin kisim i kam em meme, hos, kau, rat, pusi na dok.
Ol wel animal em ol hatpela samting long ol 'photographer' long kisim, na ol i nidim 'good luck', pasin bilong stap isi na wet, ekspiriens na gutpela ikwipmen (equipment).
Wanwan bilong ol dispela pasin bilong raun o mas long wanpela ples i go long narapela em i save stap inap long kain olsem 17-pela de.
Hap not bilong Sentinel Range i gat ol longpela maunten tru bilong Antarctica, Vinson Massif, na Mount Vinson we longpela bilong em i 4892 m.
Saltwater Crocodiles i no save stap long solwara olgeta taim, nambawan ples bilong ol long i stap em long ol maus wara we i stap long hap not long Rockhampton.
Long taim bilong ren (Novemba i go long Mas), vmak bilong wara bai i go antap na Falls bai i luk bikpela moa.
Tasol i gat planti samting long ol pisin we i luk wankain olsem ol dainaso yet.
Em i save kaikai olgeta samting we i go insait long wara; maski wanpela jaient dainaso kain olsem T. rex bai i no inap long em.
Ol han na lek bilong ol 'chimpanzee' ol i wankain long sais na longpela bilong ol, dispela i soim olsem ol i yusim han bilong ol long karim hevi bilong bodi bilong ol taim ol i wokabaut long han.
Kolpela weda (weather) ating em tasol em i wanpela trupela birua we ol lain i no redi long en bai i bungim.
Pitman i tok olsem, mak bilong bikpela bilong dispela ais, em i nogut tru long ol 'sealers' insait long 15-pela yia.
Insait long 'nomadic phase', ol 'army' anis i save mas long nait na stop long kem long de.

Ol narapela samting bilong toktok long en taim ol i bung long Bali em pasin bilong seivim ol bikbus bilong ples graun we i stap yet, na serim ol teknoloji long helpim ol kantri we i wok long divelop yet long bihainim ol rot we i no inap long mekim planti polusen (pollution) taim ol i wok long divelop.
Tropical Storm Danielle, we ol i kolim olsem namba foa 'storm' bilong 2010 Hurricane sisen (season), em i wok long redi long kirap long 'eastern' Atlantic Ocean.
I no gat wanpela "taim bilong ren" na "taim bilong san": mak bilong ren i save stap klostu wankain mak long olgeta yia.
Long stat bilong tude, ol win i wok long blo long mak kain olsem 83 km/h, na i luk olsem strong bilong em bai i wok long go daun.

Ol 'biological clock' em ol samting we i save mentenim ol yet na i save kamap ol 'electric currents' na ol i save kontinu (continue) long ron maski ol samting long autsait we i save mekim ol i ron i no stap.
Cochamó Valley -nambawan hap bilong mekim 'climbing' long Chile, em ol kolim Yosemite of South America, em i gat ol kainkain bikpela 'granite wall' na 'crag'.
Ol atoriti bilong park i tok olsem, ol lain i mas i stap 100yard/meter o moa longwe long ol bea na ol wulf na 25 yard/meter longwe long ol narapela wel animal!
Narapela samting, em animal kaikai (ol anis, ol 'termite', na kiau) em ol i isi long kaikai, na tu ol i givim bikpela mak bilong ol 'protein' we i gat olgeta ol 'amino acid' we bodi i nidim.
Wanpela eksampel em olsem, ol i no gat kon, o tomato, o potato, o kakau, na no gat wanpela bilong ol lain bilong bipo long Rom i bin teistim wanpela 'turkey'.
Ol insek em ol namba wan animal long stap long win. Dispela pasin bilong ol long flai i helpim ol long abrusim ol birua bilong ol na painim kaikai na pren bilong ol isi tru.
I go i go, na bihain long sampela tausen o milien yia, dispela tupela populesen bai luk narakain olgeta bai ol lain i no tok olsem ol i wanpela 'specie'.
Planti ol insek i ken foldim wing bilong ol i kam pas wantaim bodi bilong ol na dispela em i gutpela samting.
Planti manmeri i no ting olsem ol i wankain olsem ol dainaso bikos ol i gat 'feather' na ol i ken flai.
Ol plent (plant) i save luk nais tru insait long wel envaironmen bilong ol, olsem an no ken traim long rausim "wanpela tasol" na kisim olsem ‘specimen’.
Maski planti bilong ol animal insait long park i save long lukim ol manmeri, dispela em ol wel animal na ol lain i no ken givim kaikai long ol o distebim ol.
Ol piksa we ol i kisim wantaim 'infrared' lait i soim olsem senis we i kamap long temprita (temperature) long de na nait i soim olsem dispela ol ples em ol hul bilong ston.

Ol meme bilong we ol man i save lukautim em ol i save putim ol long grup we i save raun long ol liklik maunten o ol narapela hap bilong kaikai, planti taim ol 'goatherd' i save was long ol na dispela em ol pikinini ol bikpela man we ol i save kolim olsem 'sheperd'. Ol dispela ol pasin bilong lukautim ol meme em ol i wok long yusim yet long tude.

Ol mosasaurus i bin i stap olsem nambawan wel animal long dispela taim, no gat narapela animal i inap long kaikaim ol, olsem na ol i no pret long wanpela samting. Ol i save pret long narapela mosasaurus tasol.
Olgeta animal we i kam kamap long ailen i kam long hia taim ol i swim, flai o trip antap long wara.
Ol kalsa bilong bipo tru na ol 'tribe' i stat long lukautim ol long mekim isi long kisim milk, gras, mit na skin bilong ol.
Tude, ol insek (insect) we i no save foldim wing bilong ol em ol 'dragon flies' na ol 'mayflies'.
Taim ol manmeri i ting olsem ol 'moose' i no inap long kamapim birua, ol i ken i go klostu tumas na putim ol yet long han bilong birua.
Em i gat kainkain ol plent (plant), bikos long kainkain 'microclimate' bilong en, ol kainkain graun na level bilong graun em i stap long en.

Pasin bilong wokabaut long tupela lek em ol i painim long fosil (fossil) bilong ol Australopithecus we i bin stap 4.2-3.9 milien yia i go pinis, tasol ol Sahelanthropus i bin wokabaut long tupela lek long kain taim olsem seven milien yia i go pinis.
Ol i gat lek we i gat 'scale' na 'claws', ol i save putim kiau, na ol i save wokabaut long tupela lek olsem wanpela T-Rex.
Ol sak i stap, tasol i no save kaikai man. Planti bilong ol sak i save pret long manmeri na i save swim i go longwe.
Long arere bilong ol ‘glacier’ ol bikpela blok ais i save bruk na lus, pundaun i kam daun na kalap o rol i go longwe moa long dispela hap.
Planti ol narakain animal em i hat long painim ol, na sampela taim sampela park i gat ol lo bilong kisim foto sapos yu bai mekim mani long dispela foto.
Ol 'high winds', 'excessive precipitation', na 'wildfire' em ol sampela samtinng i ken kamap bikos long weda (weather) nogut, wankain tu em ol 'thunderstorm', 'tornado', 'waterspout', na 'cyclone'.

Dispela em i gat gras bilong pisin long olgeta hap bilong bodi bilong em, dispela pisin i save kilim ol narapela animal na ol i ting olsem em i save wokabaut long tupela lek wankain olsem Velociraptor.
Long 'savaana', em i hat long wanpela 'primate' we i gat wanpela 'digestive system' kain olsem bilong ol man long inapim ol 'amino-acid' long ol plent (plant) i stap long hap.
Ol animal tasol i gat ol brein (tasol i no olgeta animal i gat brein; eksampel, em ol jelifis (jellyfish), ol i no gat brein).
Namba tu lek bilong em i bikpela moa, dispela i mekim na em i gat dispela nem Hesperonychus we i min olsem "'western claw'."
Ol manmeri em ol i nambawan 'specie' tru we i gat pasin bilong ritim tingting bilong ol narapela.
Klostu olgeta bilong ol nambis em i seif long swim na planti bilong ol i gat gutpela seid (shade) bilong ol pohuukawa diwai long hait long san.

Ol maunten bilong Peninsula long hia i bungim wantaim ol graun i stap antap, na bihain em i stap ples klia gen na i kamapim 360 km sen (chain) bilong Ellsworth Mountains we Minnesota Glacier i brukim i go long tupela hap.
Dispela i mekim na ol i gat planti liklik ples bilong hait long ol animal we i laik kaikaim ol.
Maski ol i luk olsem ol i stap isi, ol 'bison', 'elk', 'moose', bea, na klostu olgeta bikpela animal i ken pait.

Long taim bilong winta (winter) ples i ken kol nogut tru: ol tempritsa (temperature) i no save go daun aninit long mak we ais i save kamap, tasol i win na wara i stap long win i save bung wantaim long mekim ples i pilim kol moa long wanem samting 'thermometer' i tok.
Ol dispela 'monster storm' i gat win we i spit i go long mak bilong 480 km/h (133 m/s; 300 mph).
Planti bilong ol 'paleontologists' tude i bilip olsem wanpela grup bilong ol dainaso i stap laip yet long tude. Mipela i save kolim ol olsem pisin.
Ol 'mutation' we i kamap insait long ol 'germ-line cell' tasol em ol i ken i go long ol pikinini, tasol ol 'mutation' we i kamap long narapela hap i ken kamapim 'cell-death' o kensa.
Han bilong ol man em i sot moa long lek bilong ol, na ol i gat ol 'phalange' we i stret moa.
Ol laion, 'cheetah' na 'leopard' em sampela taim ol i save sem long kam ples klia na yu bai lukim ol gut taim yu yusim ol 'binoculars'.
I bin no gat ol bikpela bus insait long graun bilong ol Canaan, olsem na plang em i ekspensif (expensive) tumas.
Ol animal we i no stap long planti hap kain olsem 'European brown bear', 'wolf', 'owl', 'lynx', 'wild cat', na 'capercaillie' i stap long hap, wantaim ol narapela animal we i stap long planti hap.

Dispela 'artistic event' em i pat bilong wanpela kempen (campaign) bilong Bucharest City Hall we i laik mekim piksa bilong kapitel bilong Romania olsem wanpela naispela siti we i gat planti gutpela samting long em.
Dispela band i kenselim (cancel) 'show' bilong ol we i bai kamap long Maui's War Memorial Stadium, we 9, 000 manmeri i laik kam long en, na ol i tok sori long ol lain i save laikim band bilong ol.
Dispela singa (singer) Sezen Aksu i pefom (perform) wantaim 'tenor' bilong Italy Alessandro Safina na singa bilong Greece Haris Alexiou.

Bihain ol ripot i tok olsem dispela balus i kisim wanpela 'bomb threat' olsem na ol salim em i go bek long Afghanistan, na em i go daun long Kandahar.
Polis i tok ol i saspek olsem wanpela soldia bilong Daesh (ISIL) i kamapim dispela hevi.
Na tu, ol i sutim tok long em long brukim lo bilong 'copyright infringement', tasol ol i no sasim em long dispela.

Wanpela dokta husat i bin wok long Children's Hospital of Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania em ol bai i sasim em wantaim 'aggravated murder' bihain long ol i painim mama bilong em i dai na i stap long baksait long kar bilong em long Trinde, ol atoriti long Ohio i tok.
Ol lain we i save kisim foto long kamera i kisim ples bilong wanpela bikmeri long wanem em i laik go long toilet. Ol i sutim Mendoza long gan na em i dai.
Bihain evidens i soim olsem Hall, wantaim 34-pela narapela ofisa bilong edukesen i bin senisim ol samting long ol test pepa, na ol i sasim ol long dispela long 2013.
California Governor Arnold Schwarzenegger i sainim wanpela 'bill' na mekim em i kamap olsem lo tru tru we i stopim ol lain long salim o rentim o geim (game) bilong pait i go long ol pikinini.
Dispela man we ol i saspek olsem em i mekim bom i pairap em ol i holimpasim, bihain long em i kisim bagarap long bodi bilong em long dispela bom i pairap.

Wanpela bom i stap long kar na i pairap long bikpela ofis bilong ol polis long Gaziantep, long Turkey aste moning na i kilim tupela polis ofisa na kamapim bagarap long bodi bilong moa long twentipela narapela manmeri.
Ol atoriti i tok olsem ol i bin mekim wanpela arest long tude na ol i no mekim sampela narapela toktok moa.
Adekoya i bin stap long Edinburgh Sheriff Court na ol i sasim wm long kilim pikinini man bilong em.

Dispela 'commisioner' i makim prais bilong 'bail', sapos em i givim, na em i mekim ol dispela sas we 'arresting officer' i tok long en i kamap olsem 'formal'. Ol dispela sas em ol bai i putim i go insait long komputa sistem bilong dispela 'state' na ol bai i gat rekod bilong dispela 'case'.

Chrstopher Garcia, wanpela mausman bilong Los Angeles Police Department, i tok olsem dispela saspela em i wanpela man na ol i wok long mekim investigesen (investigation) long em long sait bilong go insait long banis bilong narapela lain na i no long sait bilong bagarapim propeti (property).
Sampela kantri i gat bikpela panismen maski em i namba wan taim ol lain i brukim lo; ol dispela kain panismen em man bai go long kalabus long moa long 10-pela yia o dai.

Ol loya (lawyer) bilong Greece we planti lain i save long en, em Sakis Kechagioglou na George Nikolakopoulos, ol i kalabusim tupela long kalabus bilong Athens, nem bilong em Korydallus, long wanem ol i painimaut olsem ol i bin mekim 'graft' na 'corruption'.
Tripela moa bom i pairap klostu long ol bilding bilong gavman insait long tupela aua.

Taim ol lain i stap insait long ol dispela haus i tokaut long wanem samting i kamap long ol, planti bilong ol dispela famili i luksave olsem Carolyn Wilson bilong OHA i bin stilim ol 'security deposits', na em i ronawe long dispela ples.
Yu ken painimaut olsem ol i yusim yu long karim drag (drug) taim yu no save, dispela em bai mekim yu i stap insait long bikpela trabel.
Professor Pamela Ferguson bilong University of Dundee i tok olsem "ol jenelis (journalist) i ken putim ol yet long birua sapos ol i pablisim ol foto na kain samting olsem bilong ol saspek."
Ol polis i tok olsem, i luk olsem draiva bilong dispela kar we i bamim dispela man bilong kisim foto bai i no inap long kisim ol sas.
Sikspela bilong ol lain we em i holimpasim, i gat ol pikinini na lapun i stap wantaim ol, em i lusim ol i go fri pastaim, wantaim ol Filipino we i save kisim foto long kamera.

Embesi (embassy) bilong United States i stap long Nairobi, long Kenya i givim wanpela tok lukaut olsem "ol 'extremist' bilong Somalia" i wok long mekim wanpela plen long salim wanpela 'suicide bomb' long bagarapim Kenya na Ethiopia.
Dispela meri i tok, "I no gat infomesen we i tok olsem wanpela pait bai i kamap long klostu taim.
Ofis bilong gavana i tok olsem naintinpela bilong ol dispela manmeri we bagarap i kamap long bodi bilong ol, em ol polis ofisa.

Aste, pos ofis i givim wanpela tok sori bilong ol i go long ol lain bilong dispela ples na long ol lain i save ripotim nius olsem wanpela mangi i bin haitim moa long 600-pela 'postal document', wantaim 429-pela New Year postcard, we ol ino bin givim i go long ol lain bilong dispela ples.
Ol polis i tok, i luk olsem dispela bodi i stap insait long hap long kain olsem wanpela de.
Ol i tok olsem dispela man i draivim wanpela kar we i gat tripela wil (wheel) long em na i karim ol bom i go insait long grup manmeri.
Deputy Inspector General D K Arya i tok, "Mipela i bin arestim faivpela lain husat i bin reipim (rape) dispela meri bilong Switzerland na kisim mobail fon na ;eptop bilong em".
Em i stap long kastodi (custody) na i wetim 'indictment' na kot, tasol wanpela evidens bilong 'eyewitness' em i no inap long senisim wanpela samting bikos stori bilong em ol nius i pablisim pinis.
Na bikpela moa, nambawan jas Evangelos Kalousis em i stap long kalabus taim kot i painimaut olsem em i bin mekim 'corruption' na 'degenerate behaviour'.
Long Jun 28, Marshal Italo Balbo, Governor-General bilong Libya i bin dai taim em i go long Tobruk. Em i inap long kisim ples bilong Mussolini, tasol ol lain bilong em yet i abrus na i kilim em.
Rolando Mendoza i sut long M16 gan bilong em long ol turis.
Police superintendent Chandra Shekhar Solanki i tok olsem ol dispela man i karamapim pes bilong ol taim ol i kamap long kot.
Dispela em yu bai sanap long lain, bikos ol bai i no inap tok save na yusim ol dok bilong smelim drag (drug).
Dispela man husat i gat 30-pela krismas, i bon long Buffalo, em i wanpela bilong ol foapela we i bin dai long dispela 'shooting', tasol meri bilong em i no kisim wanpela bagarap.
Ol 'pirate' i bin holimpasim em na kisim ol samting bilong em, wanpela sik dok i bin kaikaim em long Tibet, em i bin ranawe long marit long Nepal na ol i arestim (arrest) em long India.
Wanpela man Filipino husat i bin wok olsem wanpela polis bipo i holimpasim ol turis bilong Hongkong taim em i kisim bas bilong ol long Manila, dispela bikpela siti bilong Philippines.
Dispela kalabus i kisim nem nogut long pasin bilong bagarapim ol kalabus manmeri taim ol US soldia i holimpasim dispela hap na ol i painimaut long dispela.

Wanpela man we i wok long skelim dispela samting i bin tok olsem Bishkek i wok long kamap long mak we "i no gat lo na oda", taim ol grup manmeri i raun long ol han rot na i stilim ol samting long ol stoa.

Dispela man bilong ritim nius long televisen, we ol i arestim em long ples we hevi i kamap, i tok olsem em i yusim longpela hap 'pole' long banisim em yet long ol botol we klostu 30-pela lain i tromoi long em.
Long 3-pela mun i go pinis, moa long 80-pela lain we ol i bin arestim (arrest) em ol i lusim ol i go fri long Central Booking senta na i no sasim ol.
Dispela jas i tokim Blake olsem em "no inap abrus" long go long kalabus.

Health Minister i tokaut long wari bilong em long gutpela bilong ol wanwan manmeri we i wok yusim ol dispela samting bikos nau yet lo i no tambu long ol dispela samting, na long ol sas we i bin kamap bikos nau dispela senis we i no bihainim mama lo i kamap.
Madhya Pradesh Police i painim dispela leptop na mobail fon we ol i bin stilim.
Ol i no save yet wanem sas bai kot i makim o wanem samting i mekim na ol atoriti i go holimpasim dispela pikinini man, tasol wok bilong kotim ol pikinini i stat pinis long kot bilong gavman.
Pasin bilong stilim ol samting long kainkain hap i kontinu (continue) long nait i kam inap long moning, na ol ofisa bilong lo i no stap long ol han rot bilong Bishkek.

Wanpela eksampel em i olsem, ol pikinini we i pilim olsem ol i kam long wanpela 'race' we ol i save tok olsem ol i no save skul gut bai i no inap long mekim gut ol skul wok bilong ol taim ol i painimaut olsem ol lain i save ting olsem long 'race' bilong ol.
Long ol 'notes' bilong em we em i yusim sampela ol toktok we ol papamama i ting olsem ol i strong tumas, na ol i ripot olsem em i save yusim tok nogut insait long klas (class).
Sekim wantaim dispela institusen, na tu sekim 'immigration department' bilong kantri yu laik stadi long en long kisim moa infomesen long ol rikwaimen.
Long ol yia bilong 1960 em i go bek long Algeria we i kisim indipendens nupela yet long tisim 'film directing'.
'Foster Care System' bilong mipela em i sapos long givim ol ples we i seif long ol pikinini long i stap, lain we i ken laikim ol na lukautim ol, gutpela helt kea (health care).
Long taim bilong dispela 'award', ol skul long Atlanta i bin i gat bikpela senis long ol test mak bilong ol.

Eksampel, long wanwan yia ol sumatin long Bennet School long North Carolina i save disainim wanpela websait long raun bilong ol i go long State Capital, na long wanwan yia dispela websait i kisim nupela stail, tasol ol olpela 'version' i save stap yet 'online' olsem wanpela 'scrapebook'.
Planti taim, yu bai wanpela 'global number' long em yet we bai larim ol PSTN fon i ringim yu. Wanem hap dispela namba i kam long en bai mekim sampela senis i kamap long ol lain i ringim yu.
Planti taim, pasin bilong enrol na go long wanpela 'gap-year course' long narapela kantru em i ken mekim ol sans bilong yu long muv i go long bikpela skul long kantri bilong yu yet i go antap.
No gat wanpela pikinini i mas stap insait long wanpela envairomen we i no gutpela long ol, i no lukautim ol, na i givim save long ol, tasol ol i save stap insait long kain envairomen olsem.
I gat tredisen (tradition) i bilong no ken slip long Easter nait na stap long wanpela ples klia long lukim san i kirap.

Dispela pes bilong websait em i isi long i go long en bikos em i gat wanpela web edres, we i mekim bai ol manmeri i ken tingim na em i isi long ol sumatin husat i save painim hat long yusim kibod o i save painim hat long speling.
Modern Education i sutim tok long em olsem em i no bin kisim tok orait na printim ol bikpela edvetismen (advertisement) long ol bas na em i bin giaman olsem em i 'chief English tutor'.
Taim dispela pasin bilong kisim save na lainim samting em i senis long dispela kain we mipela i tok long en 'base rate' we yumi save kisim save em tu i senis.
Maski, 'project based learning' i mekim pasin bilong lainim samting i kamap isi moa na i kirapim intres (interest), 'scaffolding' em i mekim moa samting.
Pasin bilong serim wanpela 'field trip' long komputa em i wanpela gutpela we tu long tingting lon wanpela raun na serim ol samting i bin kamap wantaim klas bilong bihaintaim.

Long planti kantri, yu bai nid long i gat wanpela leta i kam long dispela institusen we yu bai stadi long en, na tu yu bai nidim evidens bilong mani yu gat lontg en long sapotim yu yet long wanpela yia bilong kos bilong yu.
Tasol, Charles i go long univesiti long Trinity College, long Cambridge we em i stadim Anthropology na Archaeology, na bihain History, na em i kisim 2:2 (wanpela 'lower second class degree).
Ma em i bon long Hong Kong, na em i stadi long New York University na Havard Law School na em i bin holim wanpela "green card" bilong ol 'permanent resident' bilong America
Olsem na, taim yu ritim dispela 'grammar primer' em bai helpim yu tru long grama (grammar) bilong tok ples Persia na yu ken save gut long ol hap toktok.

Maski long dispela, olgeta lain long Belgium na Switzerland we i save yusim French i save lainim 'standard French' insait long skul, olsem na ol bai i inap long save maski yu yusim namba sistem bilong 'standard French'.

'Scaffolding' em i no wanpela metod (method) bilong lainim samting tasol em i wanpela helpim we i save givim sapot long ol wanwan sumatin husat i wok long lainim wanpela nupela samting kain olsem yusim wanpela nupela komputa o statim wanpela nupela projek (project).
Bikos ol sumatin em ol i save mekim planti toktok sapos samting i no stret, dispela sumatin we i raitim blog bai i stat long rait gut long abrusim ol toktok we i tok olsem em no rait gut.
Em i kisim treining (training) long kamap olsem wanpela 'obstetrician' na i stat long wok long Auckland's National Women's Hospital long 1959.
Planti taim bai i gat skul fi long enrol long ol dispela edukesen progrem.
Em i greduet long College of Arts & Sciences of the University of Virginia long 1950 na em i save givim bikpela mani long dispela institusen.
Em i tru olsem, i no gat wanpela gutpela samting long lainim. Pasin bilong lainim samting em i save kamap namel long sumatin na samting ol i givim em long lainim.
Sampela i ting olsem i no gat mani na ol tingting bilong yusim televisen long givim skul i senis olsem na dispela progrem i stop.

Na tu, 'blogging' "i save fosim ol sumatin long save moa long ol samting we i wok long kamap long komuniti we ol i stap long en." Dispela nid long inapim nid bilong ol lain i ritim blog bilong ol i mekim na ol sumatin i gat moa save na kamap 'interesting' (Toto, 2004).
Ol 'field trip' em ol i impoten pat bilong ol klasrum. Planti taim tisa i save laik long kisim ol sumatin bilong em i go long ol ples we ol i no inap long kalap long bas (bus) na i go.
Em i imeilim ol sumatin long lokel univesiti na kisim bikpela namba bilong ol lain i laik givim em haus long stap.
Ol 'observatory' bilong taim bipo em ol i no yusim moa long tude, na nau ol i stap olsem ol 'museum', o ples bilong edukesen.

Wanpela sumatin bilong em long bipo i tok olsem em i yusim ol 'slang' insait long klas (class), em i tisim ol long pasin bilong 'date' insait long ol skul wok em i givim, na em i olsem wanpela pren bilong ol sumatin.
Wanem samting yumi save lukim nau long sait bilong 'do-it-yourself' na givim infomesen, na lainim samting long ol 'television show' i soim dispela poin we mipela i toktok long en.
Em i mekim ol sumating i gat taim long wok long spit na mak bilong ol yet na kontrolim mak we ol i kisim tok skul.
Ol woklain i mas kisim tok orait long ol lain i antap long ol bipo long ol i mekim wanpela disisen, na ol i mas harim tok stia bilong ol lain we ol i wok aninit long en na ol i no ken askim kwesten.
'Postmodern' rot bilong lainim samting em i save givim fridom long bihainim wanpela rot tasol. I no gat wanpela gutpela wanpela we bilong lainim samting.

Karno em i wanpela tisa bilong English we planti lain i save long em na tu i no save wanbel long sampela wok bilong em we i bin tis aninit long Modern Education na King's Glory na em i bin tok olsem em i gat 9,000 sumatin taim wok bilong em kamap gut tru.

Yusim ol blog long gutpela na stretpela we "i ken mekim ol sumatin i ken skelim ol samting na save long wanem samting i no stret na wanem we bilong stret; taim ol wok wantaim ol meteriel long Internet, ol sumatin i ken save long wanem mak ol i stap long en taim ol skelim samting we ol narapela i raitim na tu ol i ken givim tingting bilong ol long ol samting we i wok long kamap (Oravec, 2002).
Long sait bilong edukesen, planti lain i bin toktok long dispela websait.
Liggins i bihainim papa bilong em na i kisim wok long sait bilong marasin.

Ol blog i ken kisim helpim sumatin long rait gut. Planti taim ol sumatin i statim blog bilong ol wantaim 'grammar' na 'spelling' we i no gutpela, na taim i gat lain bai i ritim ol bai i senis na i rait gut moa.
'Mysticism' em i wanpela rot bilong stap wantaim 'ultimate reality', 'divinity', 'spiritual truth', o God.
Moa long wan tausen yia, dispela lotu bilong ol Kristen i bin bungim ol kantri bilong Europe wantaim, maski ol i gat wanwan tok ples na kastom bilong ol yet.
Wantaim Kundalini Yoga dispela Kundalini energy ('enlightenment energy') em i save kirap insait long 'yoga postures', eksesais bilong pulim win, ol 'mantra' na 'visualizations'.
Ol manmeri bai bringim ol samting bilong mekim ofa i go long ol god na ol pris bai traim long inapim samting we ol god i nidim taim ol i mekim ol seremoni (ceremony) na ol bikpela bung bilong lotu.
Chambers, wanpela man we i no bilip long God, i tok pait olsem kot pepa bilong bilong em, em i "no bikpela samting" na "olgeta man i ken kisim narapela i go long kot."

Long dispela taim, ol i tingim bek ol taim we ol i bin mekim ol 'entrepreneurial behavior' na ol gutpela samting we i kamap i helpim ol manmeri long mekim ol nupela senis na ol nupela senis bilong lokel sios.
Planti bilong ol pasin we ol lain i save mekim long dispela holide em ol lain i no Kristen na ol kantri we i no Kristen kantri i save bihainim long olgeta hap bilong graun.
Bikos long impoten mining bilong dispela siti long sait bilong lotu, na ol hap we i stap long eria bilong Old City, Jerusalem em i wanpela hap we i save pulim planti turis.
Sikhism em i wanpela lotu bilong India. Em i stat long Punjap rijen long '15th century' taim wanpela bruk i kamap insait long tredisen (tradition) bilong ol Hindu.
Chambers i kisim God i go long kot long "dai i kamap long olgeta hap bilong graun, bagarap na pen na hevi i kamap long planti milien manmeri bilong Earth."
Nambawan lotu long Moldova em Orthodox Christian.
Insait long as tingting bilong em Tibetan Buddhism em i isi tru. Em i gat Kundalini Yoga, 'meditation' and the rot bilong 'all-embracing love'.

Muhammad i gat intres long ol samting we i bikpela moa long ol samting bilong dispela laip. Em i save go long wanpela hul bilong ston we ol i kolim olsem “Hira'” long Mountain of “Noor” (lait) long i stap na tingting.

Brazil em i kantri we i gat bikpela lain manmeri bilong Roman Catholic long Earth i stap long em, na Roman Catholic Church i save tok nogat long man i maritim man na meri i maritim meri long dispela kantri.
Tibetan Buddhism em i bihainim ol samting we Buddha i tisim, tasol ol i mekim em i go bikpela moa wantaim 'mahayana path of love' na tu wantaim planti ol teknik (technique) bilong Indian Yoga.
Olgeta lain i ken kisim 'enlightenment'. Wanpela samting tasol we i sanap namel long dispela as tingting em hevi na 'negativity' bilong yumi yet.
Alexander, taim em i king, i tok long baim ol lain long bildim gen dispela tempel, tasol ol i no larim em. Bihain, taim Alexander i dai pinis, ol i bildim gen dispela tempel long 323 BCE.

Ol Sikh i save kolim lotu bilong ol olsem Gurmat, long tok ples Punjabi dispela em i min olsem "pasin bilong 'guru'". 'Guru' em i wanpela bikpela samting insait long olgeta ol lotu bilong India, tasol insait long Sikhism 'guru' em impoten long wanem em i kamapim ol nambawan samting insait long bilip bilong ol Sikh.

Nambawan samting insait long 'Tibetan meditation' em Deity Yoga. Insait long 'visualization' bilong ol kainkain god ol rot bilong eneji i kamap klin, ol 'chakra' i kamap ektif (active) na 'enlightenment' bilong tingting i kamap.
Dispela bilding i gat sampela ol lain i raun i kam long lotu long dispela holi siti long taim bilong 'hajj pilgrimage'.
Taim yu go lukim ol 'monastery', ol meri i mas werim ol sket we i karamapim ni (knee) na tu, ol i mas karamapim ol solda (shoulder) bilong ol.
Sampela taim ol spesel taua we seip (shape) bilong ol i olsem ol 'pyramid', na ol i kolim ol 'ziggurats', em ol i save bildim olsem pat bilong ol tempel.

Sampela bilong ol bruder bilong ol Germany i laik bringim God i kam klostu long ol manmeri bilong dispela ples, olsem na ol i kamapim tok ples bilong Estonia na dispela tok ples i no gat tok piksa insait long en.
Ol lain i save stadi long 'nature' na ol 'philosophy' i save lukluk long ol 'classical texts', kain olsem, Bible long tok ples Latin.
Long dispela taim, Katolik Sios i bin i gat planti mani na pawa, olsem na ol i skelim em gut tru.
Na tu, ol Arab i bin kisim Islam i kam long ol dispela hap, na ol i kamap olsem bikpela lotu insait long Comoros na Mayotte.
Ol Sikh i save lukim bilip bilong ol olsem em i wanpela narapela lotu long Hinduism, maski ol i tokaut olsem em i kam long Hindu na sampela ol tredisen (tradition) bilong em i olsem bilong ol Hindu.
Antap long dispela taua em sampela spesol ples bilong dispela god i stap.
Ol lain long Babylon i bildim wanpela namba wan tempel long wanwan god bilong ol we ol i save mekim olsem dispela em i haus bilong dispela god.

Ol sios we i save bihainim pasin bilong lotu long bipo i save holim wanpela Easter Vigil long Sarere nai long Easter wiken, i gat ol manmeri bilong lotu i save i kam bung na ol i save mekim selebresen (celebration) long biknait i pinis na moning i kamap long amamas long Krais i kirap long dai.
Wanwan tempel i gat wanpela ples bilong sindaun autsait na i gat ples insait we ol pris tasol i ken i go insait.
Dispela man o meri we i bilip i laik i gat ekspiriens o save long 'divine realiy'/god o ol god.
Krismas em i wanpela bilong ol impoten holide bilong Christianity, na ol i save amamasim dispela de olsem bonde bilong Jisas.
Dispela siti em i holi long tripela lotu we i save bilip long wanpela God - Judaism, Christianity na Islam, na em i save stp olsem senta bilong lotu, bilip, na kalsa.
Dispela hul bilong ston, we i stap yet, i save givim klia piksa long ol bilip bilong Muhammad.
Dispela liklik ples Haldarsvík em yu ken stap long em na lukluk i go long ailan bilong Eysturoy we i stap klostu na em i gat wanpela narapela kain sios we seip (shape) bilong em i olsem 'octagon'.
